            <ol>
                <li class="mb-2 mt-2">
                    In general, the skin should be prepared by creams before and during treatment to get the best result.
                </li>
                <li class="mb-2 mt-2">
                    Treatment will be in session of 3-6 weeks interval which may extend 2-10 sessions less or more depending on results of treatment .
                </li>
